abstract: >-
  Living Architecture is a mathematical and architectural framework for AI systems
  built around living continuity rather than unlimited data accumulation. It introduces
  three coupled subsystems — SPARK (non-dissipative recurrent identity), the Temporal
  Spiral (dual-time adaptive recording), and the Field (embodied dynamics on a
  Riemannian manifold) — forming a vortex of simultaneous living dynamics.
keywords:
  - artificial intelligence
  - temporal memory
  - living architecture
  - time crystals
  - embodied AI
  - recurrent processes
  - dynamic manifold
  - dual time
